===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|lymon||citrus}}, from {{etyl|ar|en}} {{m|ar|لَيْمُون}} or {{etyl|ota|en}} {{m|ota|لیمون|tr=limon}}, from {{etyl|fa|en}} {{m|fa|لیمو|tr=limu}}<ref>{{R:Etymonline|lemon}}</ref>. Cognate with {{cog|sa|निम्बू||lime}}.

